OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,FBristol Rovers fans are calling on the
OL,7,Fclub to apologise after it released a
OL,8,Fletter referring to fans as "disabled"
OL,9,Fand "normal".
OL,11,FThe club is introducing e-tickets for
OL,12,Fseason ticket holders and is offering
OL,13,Fa physical card to supporters who do
OL,14,Fnot want to have their ticket on their
OL,15,Fphone.
OL,17,FIn the letter to its supporters' club,
OL,18,FRovers said the #15 fee for those who
OL,19,Fwant a physical season card will be
OL,20,Fwaived for disabled fans.
