OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,FBristol Rovers Disabled Supporters'
OL,7,FAssociation (DSA) said it is
OL,8,F"disappointed" in the wording used.
OL,10,F"The DSA and our club have made
OL,11,Ftremendous progress in 23/24 in areas
OL,12,Fsuch as facilities and stewarding," a
OL,13,Fspokesperson for the DSA said.
OL,15,F"We are disappointed to see (the) word
OL,16,F'normal' used in this context."
OL,18,FThey added: "One area agreed with Club
OL,19,Ffor 2024/25 is a review of comms and
OL,20,Fstyles to reflect what is current best
OL,21,Fpractice."
