OL,3,CAnger as Bristol Rovers refers to
OL,4,C'disabled' and 'normal' fans
OL,6,F"Not that I need any help but I can
OL,7,Fjust be very slow. I just feel like
OL,8,Fthe club have completely mis-worded
OL,9,Fthis awfully.
OL,11,F"I don't think they meant any harm.
OL,12,FI'd like to think they didn't mean any
OL,13,Fharm, but like I said just because
OL,14,Fyou're not in a wheelchair, doesn't
OL,15,Fmean that you don't need access to
OL,16,Fdisabled facilities or help like that.
OL,18,F"I just think the club have worded
OL,19,Fthat awfully, so do better," he added
